                            <div class="title">
                                <h2>Tradeshows</h2>
                                <p>The Trade Show will be showcasing the latest innovations from departments and agencies across the Public Service. The indoor component at 90 Elgin Street will showcase examples of excellence and innovation in how we support the government, as well as how we are building a healthy and productive workforce. The outdoor component along Sparks Street will focus on excellent service to Canadians
                                </p>
                                <h5>&rang; Read more</h5>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </a>
                </div>

                <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-4">
                    <a href="./Innovation_Fair_2017/programme#regions" class="tile-link">
                        <div class="tile background-blue-main">
                            <img src="http://www.gcpedia.gc.ca/gcwiki/images/c/c4/Innofair-toronto.jpg">
                            <div class="title">
                                <h2>Region's Zone</h2>
                                <p>More than 60% of public servants work in the regions, delivering exceptional service to Canadians. Lead by Regional Federal Councils, 10 regional Innovation Fairs will be held in 12 different cities from coast to coast to coast to feature their innovation and renewal stories.</p>
                                <h5>&rang; Read more</h5>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </a>
                </div>
                <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-4">
                    <a href="./Innovation_Fair_2017/programme#fedtalks" class="tile-link">
                        <div class="tile background-blue-main">
                            <img src="http://www.gcpedia.gc.ca/gcwiki/images/e/e7/Innofair-fedtalks.jpg">
                            <div class="title">
                                <h2>FED Talks</h2>
                                <p>FedTalks are 30 minute presentations taking place throughout the day of the Innovation Fair at 90 Elgin Street, and webcast nationally. The FedTalks address priority topics for the Public Service.</p>
                                <h5>&rang; Read more</h5>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </a>
                </div>
                <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-4">
                    <a href="./Innovation_Fair_2017/programme#workshops" class="tile-link">
                        <div class="tile background-green-1">
                            <img src="http://www.gcpedia.gc.ca/gcwiki/images/9/97/Innofair-workshops.jpg">
                            <div class="title">
                                <h2>Workshops</h2>
                                <p>An all day workshop showcasing several Departmental initiatives and programs aimed to provide Public Servants with guidance, knowledge and capabilities on how to engage and include persons with disabilities, as well as to empower persons with disabilities in the workplace.</p>
                                <h5>&rang; Read more</h5>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </a>
                </div>
                <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-4">
                    <a href="./Innovation_Fair_2017/programme#health" class="tile-link">
                        <div class="tile background-blue-2">
                            <img src="http://www.gcpedia.gc.ca/gcwiki/images/3/33/Innofair-health.jpg">
                            <div class="title">
                                <h2>Health</h2>
                                <p>Come experience the Mental Health &amp; Wellness Zone to see how public servants are changing the culture to be respectful to the mental health of all our colleagues. Join the conversation and help reduce the stigma surrounding mental health and learn about ways we can all contribute to a healthy workplace. Topics covered: Success and Bipolar Disorder, A Public Service Career after Addiction, Overcoming Anxiety, Depression and Suicide, Finding a New Normal with PTSD.</p>
                                <h5>&rang; Read more</h5>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </a>
                </div>
