                            <img src="http://www.gcpedia.gc.ca/gcwiki/images/a/a7/Innofair-recruit.jpg">
                            <div class="title">
                                <h2>Recruitment</h2>
                                <p>Come and see our Recruitment Room, one of the new features of the Innovation Fair this year, to learn about new and innovative ways departments are doing recruitment. Whether you are a student, an employee or a manager, drop by and see what’s new and happening in terms of recruitment in the public service!</p>
