                        <div class="tile background-orange-1">
                            <img src="http://www.gcpedia.gc.ca/gcwiki/images/2/26/Innofair-diversity.jpg">
                            <div class="title">
                                <h2>Living Library</h2>
                                <p>The Living Library provides public servants with an interactive opportunity to learn about the diverse experiences of their colleagues. Enabling public servants to share their experiences with one another will help build relationships and break down stereotypes contributing towards a healthier and more respectful workplace. This year, the Living Library will occur in both the morning and afternoon and consist of five genres, including “PS@150”, “Mental Health”, “Diversity and Inclusion”, “Behind the Uniform” and “Cool Jobs”.</p>
                                <h5>&rang; Read more</h5>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </a>
