                                <h2>Blueprint TV</h2>
                                <p>Health Canada is once again contributing Blueprint Television (BPTV) to the 2017 Innovation Fair. BPTV is an interview style live-streamed webcast. This year’s lineup is looking to feature exciting guests such as the Clerk, Deputy Ministers and Associate Deputy Ministers, as well as a broad range of Innovation Fair contributors. Building on last year’s success, a Crowd Correspondent will also be conducting live interviews with event participants.</p>
